<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.8.9">
<l>puntiyil camaṇar puttareṉ ṟivarka ḷottaṉa pēcavu mukantiṭ</l>
<l>ṭentaipem māṉā rimaiyavar talaiva reṇṇimu ṉiṭaṅkoṇṭa kōyil</l>
<l>cantaṉap poḻiliṉ tāḻciṉai nīḻal tāḻvarai makaḷirkaḷ nāḷum</l>
<l>mantirat tiṟaiñcum māliruñ cōlai vaṇaṅkutum vāmaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come, simple heart, we will worship in Māliruñcōlai</l>
<l rend="indent">where hill women, who linger</l>
<l>In the shade of the low boughs in sandalwood groves, bow at the shrine daily,</l>
<l>The temple where our father, the great lord, the leader of celestials</l>
<l rend="indent">choosing [it], previously took his place,</l>
<l>Truly rejoicing when even those called ignorant Jains and Buddhists</l>
<l rend="indent">say things in harmony [with us].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
